{"type": "article", "id": 55567, "title": "这套室内植物光源加湿系统，能像砌积木一样建花园｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-24T23:51:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52114, "name": "Chipp’d"}, {"id": 45758, "name": "Gantri"}, {"id": 52115, "name": "Quirino"}, {"id": 40090, "name": "SP01"}, {"id": 52116, "name": "Leandro Garcia"}, {"id": 52117, "name": "Tim Rundle"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 178, "image": "img/article/article_show/201807250022251LApmgfhNP3jSX6C.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>LeGrow - The Smart Indoor Garden For Any Space</h3><p>像砌积木一样建花园，LeGrow 是一款模块化的室内植物光源加湿系统。模块化设计，就像儿时砌积木一样，让人专注思考花园的搭建，有很多乐趣。</p><p>不管你喜欢萌萌的多肉，还是稀奇古怪的食虫草，都可以拿来种植。LeGrow 模拟太阳光每天光照 6 小时，还可以增加空气湿度，对抗空调环境下干燥，也能减少空气漂浮物。关键是它能像乐高那样组合起来，满足自由装饰搭配的需求，同时它的颜色能够让用户感到满足及平和。售价 128 元起，<a href=\"https://legrow.world.taobao.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250023242a4B39pRzVLjZUmW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250023245v7nbVqWC3jeHh6Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002324SIfKWoHpOswmPEU6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002326za1T2wXqb4QfurDi.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560714\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002326AmflkW0JCU2nVE8g.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002327SynxstXvDgAlzKdu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018072500232668GMsLzIgCuhJeRy.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002327KESmnvyD3jcohNP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002327asfwvz15mjK9OPnW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>2018 Collaboration by SP01 &amp; Tim Rundle</h3><p>创立于2016 年的澳洲设计品牌 SP01，在家具界还算是个新面孔。最近，他们与伦敦工业设计师 Tim Rundle 合作，推出 2018 合作系列，包括扶手椅、边桌以及镜子等 10 种产品，全系列的设计灵感，均是源自澳大利亚不同时代的微妙影响。</p><p>这个系列用到了一系列工业材料，比如管状钢材、玻璃、黄铜、锡制饰面、宝石色天鹅绒和经典大理石等等，精致且富有魅力。Shu-Ying 扶手椅的弧形框架，看起来有 1920 年代上海和悉尼的影子；Michelle 是一系列主打材料细节镜子；Mohana 是一系列现代风格的桌子，将大理石和玻璃以互补的形式结合在一起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002405twK3QCB4V8rezsNv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002405dpy78FgGjlR9UVea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002405cA4sikIfn1ur67pv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002405M5O6Gxwe3CoFn1lK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002405pg3Wyv24EoPCF7BA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002405youQ0BzcMemNJ2r6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002406VWRAH65xSnykCrGe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.sp01design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SP01</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Orbit Table Light by Quirino for Gantri</h3><p>总部位于旧金山的 Gantri 是一个以 3D 打印设计为主的照明工作室，其推出的最新作品，是一款名为 Orbit 的台灯，出自墨西哥蒙特雷设计工作室 Quirino 之手。</p><p>Orbit 是一款极简主义风格的台灯，可以像一个陀螺一样旋转，也有点类似于行星运行的轨道。它的好处在于引导房间四周的光线流动，体验不同区域阴影的变化。当然它也可以放在平坦的基座上，满足环境光的使用需求。</p><p>Orbit 由以玉米为原料的聚乳酸材质 3D 打印而成，然后再通过手工的方式塑造出哑光质感的柔和外观。售价 178 美元，<a href=\"https://www.gantri.com/products/10030/orbit-table-light-by-quirino?s=sm&amp;c=snow\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002510gWy7DIdrEoFQcMvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002510FTJ5yN1Epx9Q74eZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002510ETkQiFPyd5XbGfaU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002511XqI9PZfJWlcKOnG2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002511rMxS1GVhTbdEP0vB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002511VshG73ReHtznAbNZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.gantri.com/products/10030/orbit-table-light-by-quirino?s=sm&amp;c=snow\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gantri</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Toco Table by Leandro Garcia</h3><p>巴西建筑师 Leandro Garcia 最近跨足家具设计，推出一款名为 Toco 的边桌，在上个月的 MADESãoPaulo 展览上首次亮相。它由圆柱形木质底座和圆形玻璃桌面组成，可以让人透过玻璃欣赏下方木材的美感。</p><p>乍一眼看上去，玻璃桌面像是悬停在圆顶木质底座的顶部，连接两者的是黄铜垫片。 Toco 有各种形状和尺寸，也可以根据空间实际情况组合配置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018072500255528edU6xSnXyPLT7k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.179688\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002556ZaMQVmwkpRgjyIGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250025564nvDp8xYwTuoON5a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018072500255639ZlhfdCEzjavImY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.leandrogarcia.com.br/mesa-de-centro-tocos/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Leandro Garci</a>a</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Talsam by Chipp’d</h3><p>众筹平台 Kickstarter 最近上线了一款智能可穿戴首饰 Talsam，目的是解决异地恋情感无法得到有效传达的问题。你可以用它来让你爱的人知道你在想他，也可以通过它交换私人信息，甚至发送紧急求救信号。</p><p>Talsam 为两个人提供一种亲密的交流方式，好像是只属于你们的私密空间。当 Talsam 收到信息时，镶嵌其中的施华洛世奇水晶会发出自然而柔和的光芒，同时伴有震动提醒。使用者可以通过按下某个按钮发送紧急求救信号。</p><p>Talsam 提供了 6 种人造水晶石的选择，每一种都有自己独特的特性，比如亚马逊石，被认为具有镇静效果。早鸟价 99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1126199540/talsam-connect-with-a-loved-one-using-smart-jewelr?ref=u2u2bj\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002717HLMNPyZtFigwb9SX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002717MSZfw6zp3ubLIDFi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002717VGp6KIlvrDyi9SZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002717RJlayEbXNiTZe4Fq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250027170HFC2wnebJ3ATahc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250027180ljrEDtaWpb9T1qS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.512381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002719olP2Yva3Ipn1KeEJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Slide to unlock</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>“滑动解锁”——这个指令如今被视作我们使用智能手机的象征。但如果你不通过打开手机屏幕就进入完全不一样的界面。这就是韩国设计师 Hooseong Lee, Beomsic Jeon 和 Slide 开发的一个创意理念，可以净化任何预设的指令，而实现一名粉丝所希望看到的操作过程。</p><p>划过屏幕，得到进入你手机的许可。滑过屏幕正脸，滑个椭圆等到如今多种角度和范围的滑动。可以提供朝上或朝外的指示。总之，这款空气循环净化器滑动创意的特征足以撩拨你的心弦，可以在家使用好看的设计品来操作你的智能手机。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250029051Wlr57IHL2d0YhCu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002905vtE6ZpRSL1IiAonq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002905YAEgS3RmIXlWe06z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002906wfayrOFtTnWJ45ED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807250029066K4eh1lmrETNHn8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642969\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180725002906d8ymgpTBEXCIR6jF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/67028273/Slide-Air-circulator?tracking_source=curated_galleries_list\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}